List of faucets ordered by the total amount paid past hour

Finding the right faucet may be confusing with so many choices. To make it easier you may prefer to order the faucets by some specific values e.g. how much they paid.

Last Payment - when our system detected the last payment sent by this faucet. Usually the more recent this value the better, as it indicates that the faucet is popular and functioning properly.

Balance - the maximum amount the faucet is able to pay. If it is close to zero, then skip that faucet for now.

Paid (1h) - approximate total value the faucet sent to its users in the past 60 minutes.

Paid (1d) - approximate total value the faucet sent to its users in the past 24 hours.

Created - age of the faucet in days. Sorting by this value can be useful in finding new (recently created) faucets.
